===Etymology===
From {{Gr.}} ''chloro'' (green) + [[-phyta]]

===Proper noun===
'''Chlorophyta'''

#{{botany}}: A [[botanical name]] for a [[taxon]] within [[kingdom]] [[Plantae]] that includes the [[green alga]]e. The taxon is traditionally given the [[rank]] of a [[division]].

